Description: A publication-first R package for elegant bulk transcriptomics
    visualizations. The package focuses on beautiful defaults, consistent
    figure grammar, and low-friction APIs for common bulk RNA-seq plots such
    as PCA, volcano plots, heatmaps, and gene expression plots.
